snippet.title: What's Wrong With Amberlynn?
snippet.description:
The weight-loss community on YouTube is huge! With 100K+ subscribers, one of the biggest, in every sense, is Amberlynn Reid. 

Amberlynn has been at the centre of many controversies over the years, and in today’s video - after falling down a massive, gaping rabbit-hole - I attempt to find out exactly what’s wrong with Amberlynn.

Cheers for subscribing! 1 million, here I come!!!!
